📌 Title

Short-Term Stock Price Prediction Using Machine Learning

📖 Description

This project uses historical stock data to predict the next day’s closing price using regression techniques.

🎯 Objectives
Fetch stock data from API
Prepare time-series dataset
Train regression model
Compare predicted vs actual prices
🛠️ Tools & Libraries
Python
pandas
matplotlib
scikit-learn
yfinance
📂 Dataset
Stock data from Yahoo Finance
Example: Apple (AAPL), Tesla (TSLA)
▶️ Steps to Run

Install dependencies:

pip install yfinance

Load stock data using:

yf.download('AAPL')
Create target column (next day price)
Train model (Linear Regression)
Plot results
📊 Model Used
Linear Regression
📈 Output
Graph comparing:
Actual closing prices
Predicted closing prices
📉 Limitations
Does not account for market volatility
Simple model (not highly accurate)
✅ Skills Learned
Time-series handling
Regression modeling
API data fetching
Model evaluation
